{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Pahrannu un starp Totvelu/un La- \nhanu/ un Azerotu/ un Disadbu."
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Weenpadefmits Deenn- \n(Gahjumus) no Oreba pa ta \nSeira Kalna Zeffu/ lihds Rahdes \nBarneam."
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas notikke zettortodef- \nmitā Gaddā/ weenpadefmitā \nMehneti/pirmā Mehnes Deena/ \ntad runnaja Mohsus us Israēta \nBehrneem pehz wiṣu/ ko wiṣ- \nnam tas KUNGS us teem bij \npawehlejs."
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Pehz to/ kad wiṣsch bij no- \nfawis Sionu to Amoritecu Reh- \nnizu/ kas Esbonā dsihtwoja/ un \nOgu to Rehnizu no Balsana/kas \nAstarotā un Eedrejā dsihtwoja."
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wiṣṣa Jardanas puffē \neekṣch to Moabitecu Semmes/ \nsahze Mohsus scho Banftbu iṣ- \nstahsiht un sazztht."
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tas KUNGS muhsu \nDeews runnaja us mumā Ore- \nbā/ un sazzija: juhs gan ilgi ef- \nfat pee fcha Kalna kawejschees."
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Atgreescetees un zelleetees/ \nun eita to Amoritecu Kalnōs/un \npee wiṣṣem wiṣṣu Kalnimxeem \nKlajuma/ Kalnōs un Eelejā/ un \nprett Deenas-Widdu un Juhras \nMallā eekṣch Kananina Semmes/ \nun us to Lihbann/ lihds tai leelai \nUppei/ tai Uppei Wrat."
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Reds/ Es efimu to Semm \njuhsu Preekschā jums dewis/eita/ \neemantojeet to Semmi/ ko tas \nKUNGS juhsuem Tehweem \nAhbraamam/ Jhsaākam un Jeh- \nkabam swehrejs tre/ ka wiṣsch"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "wiṣṣeem/ un wiṣṣu Dsimmu- \nman pehz wiṣσeem to dohtu.\n9. Un es runnaju us jums tan- \nni Laikā/ un sazziju: Es ne war- \nru weens pats juhs paneft."
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tas KUNGS juhsu \nDeewā irr juhs wairojs/ un ran- \ngi/ juhs effat schodeen itt ka tahs \nDebbes Swaignsnes Pulkā."
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tas KUNGS juhsu Teh- \nwu Deews lai wehl pee jums pee- \nleel/ itt ka juhs nu effat tuhl- \nstofschkahrt wairak/ un tas lai \njuhs fivehti/ ittin ka wiṣsch us \njums runnajs irr."
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ka warretu es weens pats \njuhsu Gruhtumm/ un juhsu Na- \nftu/ un juhsu Bahrfchanas pa- \nnest?"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Dabbujeet preekṣch jums \ngudrus/ saprattigus un pasihsta- \nmus Wihrus/pehz juhsu Ziltim/ \nka es tohs jums par Wirfneekeem \neezeetu."
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad athildejat juhs man/ \nun sazzijat: tas irr weens labs \nWahrds/ ko tu runna/ ka tu to \ngribbi darriht."
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad nehmu es Wirfnee- \nkus no juhsahm Ziltim/ gudru- \nan pasihstamus Wihrus/ un ee \nzehlu tohs par Wirfneekeem pah \njums/ Ahwerstus/ un Kapteines \nun Wirfneekus pahr veezdefini \nteem/ un Wirfneekus pahr defini \nteem/ un Usraugus pehz juhs \nZiltim."
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un es pawehlejujuhteem So- \ngeem tanni Laikā/un sazziju: pah \nkanfajt (tahs Leetas) starp ju"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
